ocalized_name":"int","name":"int","type":"INT","links":[48]}],"title":"Length in Seconds","properties":{"cnr_id":"comfyui-easy-use","ver":"1.3.4","Node name for S&R":"easy int","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{},"version":"7.6.2"}},"widgets_values":[20]},{"id":74,"type":"MarkdownNote","pos":[-1665.616322274014,2732.0273190513917],"size":[443.8213415207274,1098.8628383621199],"flags":{},"order":11,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"properties":{"ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"version":"7.6.2","input_ue_unconnectable":{}}},"widgets_values":["# LTX 2.3 Low VRAM (8GB) + 32G Workflow\n\n## Overview\nOptimized workflow for running **LTX 2.3 (22B Distilled)** on **8GB VRAM GPUs** (e.g., RTX 3070 Laptop), focusing on stability, memory efficiency, and high-quality video/audio output.\n\n---\n\n## Required Models\n\n### Main Model\n- **LTX 2.3 – 22B (Distilled, GGUF Q4_K_M)**  \n  https://huggingface.co/unsloth/LTX-2.3-GGUF/blob/main/distilled/ltx-2.3-22b-distilled-Q4_K_M.gguf  \n\n---\n\n### Text Encoder\n- **Gemma 3 12B IT (FP4 Mixed)**  \n  https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/ltx-2/blob/main/split_files/text_encoders/gemma_3_12B_it_fp4_mixed.safetensors  \n\n---\n\n### Text Projection\n- **LTX 2.3 Text Projection (BF16)**  \n  https://huggingface.co/Kijai/LTX2.3_comfy/blob/main/text_encoders/ltx-2.3_text_projection_bf16.safetensors\n\n---\n\n### Video VAE\n- **LTX 2.3 Dev Video VAE**  \n  https://huggingface.co/unsloth/LTX-2.3-GGUF/blob/main/vae/ltx-2.3-22b-dev_video_vae.safetensors  \n\n---\n\n### Audio VAE\n- **LTX 2.3 Dev Audio VAE**  \n  https://huggingface.co/unsloth/LTX-2.3-GGUF/blob/main/vae/ltx-2.3-22b-dev_audio_vae.safetensors  \n\n---\n\n### Tiny VAE (Optional / Memory Optimization)\n- **TAE LTX 2.3**  \n  https://huggingface.co/Kijai/LTX2.3_comfy/blob/main/vae/taeltx2_3.safetensors  \n\n---\n\n## Performance Optimization\n\n### Recommended Settings\n- Install **xFormers** for improved memory efficiency and speed  \n- Use **Sage Attention** with:\n  - `fp16_triton`\n  - Enable compile  \n\n---\n\n### Torch Settings\n- Enable:\n  - `fp16 accumulation`  \n- Helps reduce VRAM usage with minimal quality loss  \n\n---\n\n## Notes\n- The **distilled model** is recommended for 8GB VRAM setups  \n- Use **Distill LoRA** only if running the **undistilled model**  \n- Tiny VAE can be used to further reduce VRAM usage (at slight quality cost)  \n\n---\n\n## Expected Max Performance (Example)\n- **Resolution:** 1600 × 900  \n- **Duration:** ~20 seconds  \n- **Generation Time:** ~20–25 minutes (RTX 3070 8GB Laptop)  \n- **Quality:** High (video + audio)"],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"},{"id":18,"type":"CLIPTextEncode","pos":[-738.1940898701729,3023.4709234670654],"size":[410,320],"flags":{},"order":19,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"clip","name":"clip","type":"CLIP","link":25},{"localized_name":"text","name":"text","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"text"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"CONDITIONING","name":"CONDITIONING","type":"CONDITIONING","links":[20]}],"title":"CLIP Text Encode (Positive)","properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.3.56","Node name for S&R":"CLIPTextEncode","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{"text":true},"version":"7.6.2","input_ue_unconnectable":{}},"enableTabs":false,"tabWidth":65,"tabXOffset":10,"hasSecondTab":false,"secondTabText":"Send Back","secondTabOffset":80,"secondTabWidth":65},"widgets_values":["A cinematic scene. Video Prompt:\n\n\"In a serene yet slightly surreal cinematic style reminiscent of indie street documentaries blended with meditative martial arts visuals, bathed in soft, diffused early morning sunlight, a fluffy orange cat stands upright on a worn wooden platform in a quiet park. The air is still except for a gentle breeze rustling nearby bamboo, casting delicate moving shadows across the ground. The cat moves with surprising grace, slowly performing Tai Chi movements—its paws flowing in controlled arcs, tail balancing each motion with precision.\n\nThe camera begins with a tight close-up on the cat’s focused eyes, reflecting calm determination, then slowly dollies back to reveal its full body as it transitions smoothly between poses. Each movement is deliberate and fluid, almost hypnotic. As it exhales, faint visible breath drifts in the cool air.\n\nCat (soft, calm voice): 'Yasuragi...'\n\nIts front paw extends forward in a slow push.\n\nCat: 'Ki no nagare...'\n\nThe bamboo behind it sways gently, leaves whispering.\n\nCat (slightly louder, centered): 'Mushin...'\n\nThe camera circles slowly, capturing the elegance of each motion as sunlight glows around the cat’s fur, creating a soft halo effect. A distant wind chime rings faintly.\n\nSuddenly, the microphone dips slightly into frame, as if an unseen interviewer is unsure whether to interrupt.\n\nInterviewer (whispering, confused): '...Is it... teaching something?'\n\nThe cat pauses mid-pose, one paw raised, eyes half-lidded.\n\nCat (without breaking form): 'Kokoro o shizume...'\n\nA long silence follows as the camera lingers. Then the cat slowly completes the movement, tail flicking with quiet authority.\n\nInterviewer (awkward): 'Right. Yeah. We’re definitely not qualified for this.'\n\nThe camera tilts upward slightly as sunlight filters through the trees, illuminating drifting leaves while the cat continues its Tai Chi, completely undisturbed.\""],"color":"#232","bgcolor":"#353"},{"id":30,"type":"LTXVChunkFeedForward","pos":[612.0780990021934,2783.5058019363],"size":[289.74165131432335,89.31995204345503],"flags":{},"order":30,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"model","name":"model","type":"MODEL","link":27},{"localized_name":"chunks","name":"chunks","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"chunks"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"dim_threshold","name":"dim_threshold","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"dim_threshold"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"model","name":"model","type":"MODEL","links":[39,80]}],"properties":{"aux